simulation.engine
Class CollisionShape

java.lang.Object
  simulation.engine.CollisionShape
Direct Known Subclasses:
CollisionCircle, CollisionPolygon
public abstract class CollisionShape
extends java.lang.Object

A shape that can be tested to see if it collides with another shape. There are only circles and polygons.

Author:
Jacob Taylor
